name: Artificial I - Periodical Self Portrait(vid1)
description: Trying to capture not just one self but the varieties one exhibits, Dornig created an approximation of his behavior by recording hundreds of hours of himself in front of his computer during the beginning of the pandemic in Shanghai around March 2020. The dataset was then used with the Machine Learning algorithm StyleGan2.
